<h1 class="entry-title" itemprop="name"><a class="topic" href="/journaux">Journal</a> <a href="/users/fravashyo/journaux/la-drole-d-histoire-de-john-mcafee">La drôle d&#39;histoire de John McAfee</a></h1>
<div class="meta">
Posté par <a href="/users/fravashyo" rel="author">fravashyo</a> (<a href="http://www.bitvisitor.com/?ref=1Bqv4vkYeLf9xf8PF4hHvjVNRHKEAMrWrU">page perso</a>) <time class="updated" datetime="2012-11-20T16:33:58+01:00"><span class="date">le 20/11/12</span> <span class="time">à 16:33</span></time>.
