<h1 class="entry-title" itemprop="name"><a class="topic" href="/journaux">Journal</a> <a href="/users/fravashyo/journaux/ice-cream-sandwich-je-ne-mange-pas-de-ce-pain-la">ice cream sandwich, je ne mange pas de ce pain-là</a></h1>
<div class="meta">
Posté par <a href="/users/fravashyo" rel="author">fravashyo</a> (<a href="http://www.bitvisitor.com/?ref=1Bqv4vkYeLf9xf8PF4hHvjVNRHKEAMrWrU">page perso</a>) <time class="updated" datetime="2012-10-25T23:24:18+02:00"><span class="date">le 25/10/12</span> <span class="time">à 23:24</span></time>.
<a href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/3.0/deed.fr" rel="license">Licence CC by-sa</a>
<div class="tags">
Tags :
<ul class="tag_cloud" itemprop="keywords">
<li><a href="/tags/android/public" rel="tag">android</a></li>
<li><a href="/tags/tablette/public" rel="tag">tablette</a></li>
<li><a href="/tags/zenithink/public" rel="tag">zenithink</a></li>
<li><a href="/tags/trolldi/public" rel="tag">trolldi</a></li></ul>
